subject: Unable to reset password
body:
Hi support,

I’m unable to reset my password. Can you please help me,  this is very urgent. Every time I click the reset link, I get an error saying the token is invalid.

Can you help me regain access to my account?

Thanks,
Casey

subject: Dashboard shows blank screen
body:
Hello,

After logging in today, my dashboard loads but shows a blank screen with no data.

Is this a known issue or something on my end?

Best,
Jordan

subject: File upload fails with error
body:
Hi,

Whenever I upload a CSV file, the system returns an error and the upload fails.

Please advise how to fix this.

Thanks,
Morgan

subject: Account access issue
body:
Support team,

I’m locked out of my account and keep seeing an access denied message.

Can you help troubleshoot?

— Riley

body:

After yesterday’s update, one of the main features no longer works as expected.

Thanks,
Sam

Hello billing,

My latest invoice includes a charge I don’t recognize.

Can you explain what this charge is for?

Thanks,
